      'Narrated `Aisha: Once I saw Allahs Messenger (sallallahu alaihi wa sallam) at the door of my house while some Ethiopians were playing in the mosque (displaying their skill with spears). Allahs Messenger (sallallahu alaihi wa sallam) was screening me with his Rida so as to enable me to see their display. (`Urwa said that `Aisha said, I saw the Prophet (sallallahu alaihi wa sallam) and the Ethiopians were playing with their spears.)',
