    hadithEnglish:
      'Narrated Abu Huraira: I heard Allahs Messenger (sallallahu alaihi wa sallam) saying, If there was a river at the door of anyone of you and he took a bath in it five times a day would you notice any dirt on him? They said, Not a trace of dirt would be left. The Prophet (sallallahu alaihi wa sallam) added, That is the example of the five prayers with which Allah blots out (annuls) evil deeds.',
