    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Humaid:\n\nAnas was asked, Did Allahs Messenger (s) wear a ring? He said, Yes. Once he delayed the `Isha prayer till midnight and after the prayer, he faced us and said, The people prayed and have slept and you remained in prayer as long as you waited for it.  Anas added, As if I were just now observing the glitter of his ring.',
