    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Malik Ibn Buhaina:\n\nAllahs Messenger (s) passed by a man praying two rak`at after the Iqama (had been pronounced). When Allahs Messenger (s) completed the prayer, the people gathered around him (the Prophet) or that man and Allahs Messenger (s) said to him (protesting), Are there four rak`at in Fajr prayer? Are there four rak`at in Fajr prayer?',
