    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Jabir bin Samura:\n\nSa`d said, I used to pray with them a prayer similar to that of Allahs Messenger (s) (the prayer of Zuhr and `Asr) reducing nothing from them. I used to prolong the first two rak`at and shorten the last two rak`at. `Umar said to Sa`d This was what we thought about you.',
