    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated `Aisha:\n\nThe Prophet (s) used to say in his bowing and prostrations, Subhanaka l-lahumma Rabbana wa bihamdika; Allahumma ghfir li. (Exalted [from unbecoming attributes] Are you O Allah our Lord, and by Your praise [do I exalt you]. O Allah! Forgive me).',
