      ' Narrated Um Salama:\n\n(the wife of the Prophet) In the lifetime of Allahs Messenger (s) the women used to get up when they finished their compulsory prayers with Taslim. The Prophet (s) and the men would stay on at their places as long as Allah will. When the Prophet (s) got up, the men would then get up.',
